data.description: Welcome to your perfect home in a peaceful neighbor-friendly subdivision, where the allure of modern living meets the charm of community amenities. This splendid property, just 3 years young, is adorned with upgrades that redefine comfort and style.  No builder grade appliances here!  All kitchen appliances have been replaced by the owner.  Step into a kitchen transformed by top-of-the-line appliances, a true culinary haven. Featuring a new gas double oven stove/range, a whisper-quiet dishwasher, and a built-in microwave. Bid farewell to high energy bills, thanks to the solar panels that gracefully crown your roof, promising an average electric bill of only $70 per month. Remote garage door access adds convenience. Indulge in the luxury of pure water with Rainsoft water softener and a Reverse Osmosis (RO) system at the kitchen sink. Enjoy the soft water in the updated and luxurious primary bathroom shower! Outdoor living is elevated with an extended concrete patio in the backyard, a retreat for relaxation and entertainment. The sprawling corner lot is effortlessly maintained with the convenience of a sprinkler system.  Vacation at home and make lots of memories with the delights of miles of walking trails, a splash pad, 3 pools, sports court, and play area, a well-equipped fitness center, natural areas and parks, and even a fishing pond creating a vibrant community hub. Revel in the pride of ownership evident in every corner of this home, from the upgraded interior to the attractive curb appeal. In a cookie-cutter world, this  home is not like any others with the relaxing wall colors that infuse the interior with added character. Picture yourself sipping morning coffee on the front porch, greeted by a pleasant and warm sunrise while you snuggle under the cover of a cozy jacket. The neighborhood complements this lifestyle with a country feel, yet it's close to shopping, schools, and dining. Enjoy the convenience of excellent Smithson Valley schools. This isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle. Embrace year-round outdoor activity on the maze of neighborhood walking trails. Step into a life where modern elegance, timeless charm, and community amenities converge seamlessly. Welcome home!
